videos.description: Minnesota's Michael Hurt kicks it out to Gaston Diedhio who sinks the jumper.
videos.headline: Golden Gophers' Diedhiou drains nice jumper

videos.description: Boilermakers' Carsen Edwards double-crosses a Golden Gopher and drains a 3-pointer from the top of the arc.
videos.headline: Purdue's Edwards swishes in 3-pointer

videos.description: Purdue's P.J. Thompson intercepts a pass and chucks it to Vincent Edwards, who stuffs it in for a dunk.
videos.headline: Boilermakers' Edwards with a leak-out dunk
